<item>
            <title>[BATCH-170] Concurrent modification of StepExecution when running an asynchrounous step operation</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-170</link>
                <project id="10090" key="BATCH">Spring Batch</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Use of a hibernateJobDao eventually results in a StaleObjectStateException when running an asynchrounous step operation:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;myStepExecutor&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.batch.execution.step.simple.SimpleStepExecutor&quot; scope=&quot;prototype&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;property name=&quot;transactionManager&quot; ref=&quot;txManager&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;property name=&quot;repository&quot; ref=&quot;simpleJobRepository&quot; /&amp;gt;  &lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;property name=&quot;stepOperations&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;bean class=&quot;org.springframework.batch.repeat.support.TaskExecutorRepeatTemplate&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;taskExecutor&quot; ref=&quot;threadPoolTaskExecutor&quot;/&amp;gt;        &lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;    &lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=44884&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=44884&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
