                            <comment id="28544" author="david_syer" created="Tue, 18 Dec 2007 04:53:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The Hibernate*Daos have been removed, but the problem is still there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28570" author="david_syer" created="Wed, 19 Dec 2007 00:01:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated SqlStepDao to check optimistic locking, and synchronized access to the step execution so that multiple threads can share a single instance.  If anyone wants to test it more extensively, that would be great (I used parallelJob.xml from the samples).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
